      <section class="promo-section">
        <div class="promo-card">
          <div class="promo-content">
            <h3>Real-time Location Traking</h3>
               <p>
             WeWalk utilizes advanced GPS technology to accurately track your real-time location, 
             providing your loved ones with the peace of mind they deserve by knowing exactly where 
             you are at any given moment. 
             </p>
             <p>
             Our cutting-edge discreet call feature enables you to silently 
             call for help and swiftly share your precise location with the simple touch of a button. 
            </p>
          </div>
          <br />
        </div>
        <div class="promo-card">
          <div class="promo-content">
            <h3>Emergency Alerts</h3>
            <p>
              With WeWalk, you can effortlessly and quickly send emergency 
              alerts to your chosen contacts or directly to the nearest local authorities, ensuring 
              that they receive timely notifications about your situation. 
            </p>
             <p>
              This prompt communication includes sharing your precise location and identifying the type of potential danger. 
              It enables a rapid and coordinated response to any such threat you might encounter.
            </p>
          </div>
           <br />
        </div>
        <div class="promo-card">
          <div class="promo-content">
            <h3>Community Support</h3>
            <p>
            Join a vibrant and caring community where you'll have the opportunity to share not only safety tips but also 
            personal experiences and valuable support. We're excited to introduce a new feature: the ability to find 
            active users near you and connect with them for a shared walking experience.
            </p>
            <p>
            Your active involvement amplifies the positive impact we can make, ensuring that each user feels empowered and 
            supported.
            </p>
          </div>
          <br />
        </div>
